Shortcake
  --Mary Nolan

2 tbsp sugar
2 c ap flour
2 tsp baking powder
1/2 tsp baking soda
3/4 tsp salt
1 1/2 c heavy cream

Preheat oven to 400F Sift together the flour, baking powder, baking soda, sugar, and salt in a medium bowl. Add heavy cream and mix until just combined. Place mixture in an ungreased 8" square pan and bake until golden, 18-20 min. Remove shortcake from pan and place on a rack to cool slightly.
